# 0ratoria

A speech analysis application that helps users improve their oratory skills through interactive exercises and real-time feedback.

**Platanus Hack 2025**

## Overview

0ratoria is a full-stack application that analyzes speech patterns and provides detailed metrics to help users enhance their public speaking abilities. Users complete three types of exercises (reading, description, and Q&A) and receive comprehensive feedback on their performance.

## Features

- ğŸ¤ **Audio Recording**: Record your speech directly in the browser
