  - Transcription precision
- ğŸ“± **Progressive Web App**: Installable PWA for easy access
- ğŸ¯ **Interactive Exercises**: Three exercise types to practice different speaking skills

## Tech Stack

### Backend
- FastAPI (Python)
- ElevenLabs API (Speech-to-Text)
- spaCy (NLP for Spanish)
- Docker

### Frontend
- React + TypeScript
- Vite
- Tailwind CSS
- React Router

